//App Request: post, get, delete, patch, put

//Deploy checklist
First time:
    Create Heroku acc
        Commit codebase to git
            Install Heroku CLI and Create App
                Deploy App with git
                    Heroku deploys projects

Subsequent deploys
    Commit cobase to git
        Deploy App with Git

//HEROKU NOTES
//FIRST TIME
check version:  heroku -v
login:          heroku login

create new:     heroku create     
add git repo:   git remote add heroku https://git.heroku.com/morning-fjord-46167.git
(#link up there is just an example)

Deploy:         git push heroku master
Open Server:    heroku open
View Log:       heroku logs

//Subsequent
check status:   git status
add         :   git add
commit      :   git commit -m "this this description are for the commit, you must add something useful. It is possible to leave empty space"
push        :   git push heroku master